kaboom is a 2010 american science fiction mystery fantasy comedy film written and directed by gregg araki and starring thomas dekker , juno temple , haley bennett , and james duval .   a science fiction story centered on the sexual adventures of a group of college students and their investigation of a bizarre cult , the film premiered at the 2010 cannes film festival , where it was awarded the first ever queer palm for its contribution to lesbian , gay , bisexual or transgender issues .